Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.80,0:03:48.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想著  "我爸爸打死了小鹿斑比"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Like, "My dad just shot Bambi."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:51.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一段時間之后  他就再也不帶我去打獵了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}After a while, he stopped taking me hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.20,0:03:53.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟爸爸說好  等我長大之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I made a deal with my dad, growing up,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會嘗試各種不同的運動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that I would try all different sports.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他打過棒球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He tried baseball.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.60,0:04:00.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打過籃球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He tried basketball.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:01.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都打過\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He tried them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.33,0:04:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得有一次他們輸了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I remember one loss they had,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:06.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad2\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\4c&H000000&\fad(800,800)\pos(40.167,218.507)}戴維 {  \fn方正蘭亭黑_GBK\fs20}謝恩的父親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝恩根本沒怎么上場  可他難過極了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and Shane hardly played at all, but, boy, he took it hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.02,0:04:08.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的特別可愛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And that was pretty cute,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.27,0:04:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他算不上優秀的球員\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but he wasn't much of a contributor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.73,0:04:14.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我對謝恩的第一印象是在學校舞臺劇上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My first memory of Shane was at a school play,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.06,0:04:14.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad2\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\4c&H000000&\fad(800,0)\pos(38.967,218.507)}塔米 {  \fn方正蘭亭黑_GBK\fs20}鄰家母親
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.97,0:04:16.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在臺上唱歌跳舞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and he was just singing, dancing --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.77,0:04:19.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,使出渾身解數來逗大家開心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}whatever he could do to entertain, he was doing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.65,0:04:23.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們用紅色亮片做了一輛車\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We had made a car. We used red glitter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝恩的眼中就只有那輛車\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And Shane wanted that car like none other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他四年級的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was in fourth grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.35,0:04:30.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得他跟老師說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and I remember him telling his teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:33.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他高中畢業后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that, when he graduated from high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要去加利福尼亞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}he was going to California.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.28,0:04:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想  "為什么"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I just thought, "Why is that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.65,0:04:39.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那真的很奇怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You know, that just seemed so strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.96,0:04:42.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad2\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\4c&H000000&\fad(0,0)\pos(38.967,217.707)}米凱拉 {  \fn方正蘭亭黑_GBK\fs20}謝恩的發小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.26,0:04:42.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他唱芭芭拉·史翠珊歌的樣子我仍記憶猶新\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I particularly remember him singing Barbra Streisand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.80,0:04:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在屋里不停繞著圈跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was running around the room in circles
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.57,0:04:45.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當著每個人的面唱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and singing right in everyone's face --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.63,0:04:47.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad2\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\4c&H000000&\fad(0,800)\pos(38.967,217.707)}米凱拉 {  \fn方正蘭亭黑_GBK\fs20}謝恩的發小
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.99,0:04:48.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,?你沒有送花給我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}♪ You don't bring me flowers
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.32,0:04:51.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常迷人  特別無畏\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Like, just so charismatic and so unafraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.34,0:04:53.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上小學的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I was in elementary school,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有時候會做那樣的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and what I would do sometimes is --
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.82,0:04:55.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想上床睡覺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I didn't want to go to bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.86,0:04:57.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而媽媽讓我去睡覺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and my mom would tell me to go to bed,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.24,0:04:58.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我就偷偷溜下床\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and then I would sneak out
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:05:01.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坐在她的躺椅后面看電視\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and sit behind her recliner and watch the TV,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:03.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我想叛逆一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}'cause I wanted to kind of be a little rebel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:05.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一次  她在看《費城故事》\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}One time, she was watching the movie "Philadelphia."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.95,0:05:08.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到電影結束的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Finally, it got to the end of the movie,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.50,0:05:10.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道那個男的是同性戀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and I knew that this guy was gay,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:11.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他病了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and I knew that he was sick
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:14.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且因為同性戀的身份  他就快死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and he was dying because of being gay,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.55,0:05:16.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那深深地引起了我的共鳴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and that really -- it struck a chord with me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.96,0:05:21.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我意識到  我就和他一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}'cause I knew that...I was like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.24,0:05:23.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他喜歡上了另一個男人  結果瞧瞧發生了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That guy liked another guy, and look what happened --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.88,0:05:26.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他越來越消瘦  越來越虛弱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}he kept getting thinner, he kept getting pale,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.11,0:05:28.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的臉上  身上都長滿了膿瘡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And there was like sores on his face and his body,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得當時在想  "這就是我今后的模樣"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and I just remember thinking that, "That's gonna be me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.61,0:05:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我也會變成這樣"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's gonna happen to me."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他變得比以前安靜了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He got quieter,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.09,0:05:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也沒那么有趣了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and he wasn't as fun to be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.20,0:05:43.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能看得出他有心事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You could tell that something was always on his mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.86,0:05:45.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad2\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\4c&H000000&\fad(800,800)\pos(40.167,218.507)}莉茲 {  \fn方正蘭亭黑_GBK\fs20}謝恩的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.09,0:05:44.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有些事一直在困擾著他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Something was always bothering him,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但你就是不知道是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but you never knew what it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天晚上  我記得謝恩走進我的房間\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}One night, I remember Shane coming into my room,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.70,0:05:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說  "媽  我要死于艾滋病了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and he said, "Mom, I'm dying of A.I.D.S."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.59,0:05:55.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我問  "親愛的  為什么這么說"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I said, "Honey, why are you saying that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.97,0:05:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說  "因為電影是這么演的"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and he goes, "Well, because of that movie."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.85,0:06:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告訴他  "親愛的  你沒有艾滋病"  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I said, "Well, honey, you don't have A.I.D.S."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:03.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時我才真正注意到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And that's when I really noticed
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:05.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝恩得了焦慮癥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Shane starting to have panic attacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.17,0:06:11.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad2\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\4c&H000000&\fad(800,800)\pos(78.728,242)}帕特 {\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs20}謝恩的曾祖母                        {\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\fs24}朱迪 { \fn方正蘭亭黑_GBK\fs20}謝恩的祖母
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.47,0:06:07.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他感覺無法呼吸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He felt like he couldn't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.45,0:06:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不得不跟他說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And we would have to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"你得往頭上套個袋子"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}"You've got to put a sack over your head."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.21,0:06:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs15\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}吸入二氧化碳可以平衡恐慌發作時體內酸堿度  防止過度呼吸導致的呼吸性堿中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.27,0:06:13.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不喜歡那樣做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He didn't like doing it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.26,0:06:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但如果是在我家  我們就會給他套個袋子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but when he was at my house, we put a sack over his head.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.80,0:06:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨著時間推移\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So as time went on,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.89,0:06:21.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會偷偷溜進家里的某間臥室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I would sneak into one of the bedrooms in our house
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.51,0:06:24.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后撥911  說我快死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and I would dial 911 and tell them that I was dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.17,0:06:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,突然間\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.79,0:06:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看見車道上有很多燈在閃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I see these flashing lights in the driveway,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.26,0:06:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就想  "出什么事了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and I thought, "What is going on?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.11,0:06:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上樓之后  急救人員說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I go upstairs, and here is the ambulance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.08,0:06:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,家里有人遇到麻煩了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}saying that somebody is in distress in this home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.18,0:06:37.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人噎住了  有人窒息了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Somebody was choking. Somebody was suffocating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她就會說  "謝恩  該死的"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It led to her being like, you know, "Shane, god damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.38,0:06:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"警察怎么又來了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The cops are here again."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.87,0:06:45.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從他六年級開始一直到高中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}From sixth grade, till I got that kid through high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.06,0:06:46.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都不知道自己是怎么撐下來的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I didn't know if I was gonna survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.36,0:06:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我敢說他報了10到15次警\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I bet 10, 15 times he called 911.
