Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.94,0:10:31.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種人們見到就會說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that people are like, "Ooh!
