Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.28,0:10:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我只在自己家的跑步機上跑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but when I run, it's on a treadmill in our house,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.47,0:10:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為我不想讓人看到我跑步的樣子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}because I do not want people seeing me running.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.54,0:10:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全不想讓別人看到我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I do not want people to see me, really, at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:46.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事我一直很渴望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The one thing that I wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.53,0:10:50.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是有一個愿意和我聊天交朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}was just someone that I could talk to and relate to,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.32,0:10:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并接受真實自我的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that accepted me for being me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.57,0:10:57.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾迷戀上了一個叫馬特·帕克的男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I developed a crush for a guy named Matt Parker.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.57,0:11:00.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可以整晚待在彼此的家里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And we would spend the night at each other's houses all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起出門打籃球\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We would play basketball outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是最好的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We were just best friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:08.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了高中  我終于鼓起勇氣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was in high school that I finally got the courage
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告訴馬特我的感受  我給他寫了封情書\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to tell Matt how I felt, and I wrote him a love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.17,0:11:13.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很緊張\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I was nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:17.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寫情書這事我真的很緊張\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I was so nervous about giving him the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.33,0:11:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他告訴我他不是同性戀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But he had to tell me that he's not gay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.47,0:11:22.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很傷心  但同時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And it broke my heart, but at the same time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.64,0:11:26.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也很高興  因為他愿意繼續做我朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I was still so happy that he was willing to be my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:29.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當時高中里有這么幾個人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}There was a situation with a couple friends in high school,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.54,0:11:31.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們質疑他的性向\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and they were questioning his sexuality
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.33,0:11:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad2\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\4c&H000000&\fad(800,0)\pos(38.967,214)}斯科特 {  \fn方正蘭亭黑_GBK\fs20}謝恩的高中朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:32.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且...  嘲笑他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and kind of were, you know, mocking him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.93,0:11:33.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿他開玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}making fun of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.59,0:11:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的幾個朋友也對他避之不及\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And a couple of his friends completely shunning him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:38.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接到他好朋友母親的電話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I got a phone call from one of his best friend's mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.86,0:11:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她想讓我過去一趟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and she wanted me to come over.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很生氣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She was very upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.11,0:11:43.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當我媽告訴我她要去馬特家時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Once my mom told me that she was going over to Matt's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.63,0:11:45.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我立刻預感到這不會是好事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I knew immediately this was not gonna be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.62,0:11:48.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也算不上一封真正意義上的情書\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It wasn't, you know, really a love, love letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.68,0:11:50.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是寫了他很欣賞馬特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was just, you know, he admired Matt,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.54,0:11:52.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡和他在一起的時光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}he enjoyed his time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.73,0:11:56.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我看來更像是一封宣誓友誼的信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and it was just, I thought, like a good friendship letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.03,0:11:57.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有讓人反感的文字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was nothing distasteful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:11:59.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和性無關\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was nothing sexual.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.52,0:12:03.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是說了他對他的感覺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was just telling him how he felt about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.27,0:12:05.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我讓她說完了她想說的話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I let her say everything she wanted to say,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后我告訴她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and after she was done, I just told her,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:09.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  "你不用再擔心了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I said, "You'll never have to worry about this again,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.15,0:12:10.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"因為謝恩不會再和馬特一起玩了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}because Shane will never be around Matt,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.83,0:12:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我也不想再跟你有什么聯系"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and I don't want to ever hear from you again."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:13.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不想復述我對她說的原話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't want to say what I really told her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.95,0:12:16.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那不太禮貌  我大概是告訴她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It wasn't polite, and I just told her, basically,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.34,0:12:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離我們遠點  別騷擾我兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}take the flying leap and to leave my son alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.13,0:12:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬特的父母在社區里很有地位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Matt's parents were very prominent in the community.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.62,0:12:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他父親是校長\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}His dad was a principal.
