Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.73,0:12:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,校長告訴我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I was told by the principal
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.14,0:12:27.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不得參加\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that I wasn't allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.95,0:12:29.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何體育比賽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to go to any sporting events,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.52,0:12:31.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為馬特在隊里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Because Matt was on the teams.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:33.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是塊大場地\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That was the big place to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.43,0:12:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鎮上所有的人都會去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That was where everyone in town was,
