Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝恩也因此無法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and Shane wasn't able
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.11,0:12:44.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟小伙伴們一起參加一次重要的旅行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to go on a very important trip with his youth group.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為馬特的父母不允許他去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Matt's parents made it so he couldn't go,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.04,0:12:48.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他為那次旅行攢了許多錢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and he had raised all this money to go on this trip,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.97,0:12:50.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他很絕望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and he was devastated.
