Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.24,0:12:53.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但能看出來他很受打擊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but you could tell he was hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.28,0:12:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情書發出去之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Once this letter came out,
