Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.87,0:13:21.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此在那里生活很難\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So it's a tough place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.41,0:13:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在他被禁止參加這些活動前  \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Before he was banned,
