Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.68,0:13:44.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  "把那該死的獎杯放下  離他遠點"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I said, "You put that damn cup down, and leave him alone."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.51,0:13:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看著這種事發生在我兒子身上太讓人心疼了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was just heartbreaking to see that happen to my son.
