Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.07,0:13:51.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在與馬特和他家人的種種鬧劇結束后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was after all the drama with Matt and his family
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.33,0:13:55.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的心情十分陰暗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that I just went to a really dark place,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.00,0:13:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我崩潰了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and I had a breakdown.
