Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.00,0:14:03.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其他孩子讓他生不如死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Other kids made his life literally a living hell,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:05.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且毫無好轉跡象\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and it never really got better,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.96,0:14:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為他也看不到希望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I don't think he ever saw it would get better,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.22,0:14:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他直接不去上學了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and that's why he just stopped going.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.07,0:14:13.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一天晚上  我和三個女兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}One evening, all three daughters and I
