Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.21,0:14:16.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天是他的生日\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and it was his birthday,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.59,0:14:20.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是孤零零地跟媽媽逛街\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And he was by himself, just hanging out with his mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.83,0:14:22.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的情緒很低落\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was very depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.47,0:14:24.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不再是以前那個謝恩了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was not shane.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:26.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像變成了一具空殼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was like a shell of himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.75,0:14:29.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我為自己給家人帶來的難堪與傷害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I was sick of the embarrassment and the pain
