Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.77,0:14:31.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感到深深的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that I was bringing to my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.14,0:14:35.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得唯一能讓他們解脫的辦法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I felt like the only way that I can make their lives better
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.24,0:14:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是獨自一人去面對\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}is by taking my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.66,0:14:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天在爸爸的住處  只有我一個人在家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I was at my dad's house, I was home alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我走到他放槍的地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I just walked over to his gun case.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:49.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,取出了一把槍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I took one of the guns,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.63,0:14:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后回到了客廳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I just went back in the living room,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.31,0:14:53.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我拿著槍  坐在那兒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I just sat there, and I held it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想了很多很多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I mean, there was so many thoughts,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.42,0:14:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時  我腦子里一片混亂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}like, going through my head at that moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.20,0:14:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我苦苦掙扎了一個多小時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was like for over an hour, just really contemplating,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.74,0:15:01.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做著艱難的抉擇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}like, what my next step should be.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.34,0:15:04.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還好  我意識到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Fortunately, I also thought through
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,選擇死亡對我的親人太不公平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}in that it wouldn't be fair to my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.98,0:15:08.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我媽媽也不公平\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It wouldn't be fair to my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.43,0:15:10.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不得不考慮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I just had to visualize
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.40,0:15:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我就這樣結束了自己的生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}what the experience would be like for them
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:13.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的家人會遭受怎樣的痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}if I did take my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.96,0:15:17.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這不值得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And it wouldn't be worth it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.18,0:15:21.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同樣在某程度上  我相信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Also, on some level, I must have believed
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:24.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總會有那么一天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that, somehow, someday,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:26.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會出現這么一個人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}there's gonna be someone out there
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他會很單純地愛上我這個人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}who's gonna love me for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:37.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆就是有這樣的氣質\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Tom just had this presence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充滿活力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He had this energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.57,0:15:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他總是不停地唱啊跳啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was always singing and laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,享受生活\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and enjoying life so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.49,0:15:45.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}?軍功卓著的將軍有顆金子般的心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}♪ There was a decorated general with a heart of gold
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.88,0:15:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad2\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\4c&H000000&\fad(1000,1000)\pos(40.167,238)}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs18\fsp0.5}演唱: 湯姆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:47.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是班里的佼佼者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was at the top of his class.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:51.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無論是體育運動  還是學校功課\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was a leader in all aspects of the word,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.02,0:15:54.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他總是門門全優\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}in sports, and in school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}?在戰場上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}♪ On the battlefield...
