Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.81,0:16:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad2\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\4c&H000000&\fad(800,800)\pos(130.142,236)}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs20}湯姆在柯爾沃軍事學院的好友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.95,0:15:57.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每次見到湯姆的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Every time you met Tom,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:16:00.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像見到了自己最好的朋友一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}it felt like you were meeting your best friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.24,0:16:01.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不管你是誰\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And it didn't matter who you were --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他總是無條件支持你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He always had your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.46,0:16:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為湯姆沒有去本地的高中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I think Tom went to Culver
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:07.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是選擇了柯爾沃\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}instead of the high school in his hometown,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.63,0:16:09.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為他覺得這是個\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}because he saw it as an opportunity
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:11.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開闊眼界的機會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to open his horizons,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.50,0:16:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為此  他的父母功不可沒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And, you know, his parents played a big role in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.93,0:16:16.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他媽媽在柯爾沃工作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}His mom worked at culver,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此他們才能支付減免的學費\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}primarily so that they could afford the reduced tuition,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:22.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此湯姆才有了以后那些機會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}so that Tom would have all those opportunities.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高三那年  他向我吐露心聲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He came out to me our senior year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天晚上  我們坐在草地上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was at night, and we were sitting in the grass,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:30.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只記得  他突然變得很嚴肅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and I remember he got really serious all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.64,0:16:32.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說  "我有事要告訴你"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And he said, "I have something to tell you --
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:34.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我是同性戀"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm gay."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.49,0:16:36.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后他就把頭埋了下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Then he put his head in his lap,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哭了出來  他的情緒很激動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And he was crying and really emotional about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.09,0:16:40.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想他真的很害怕被人說三道四\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I think he was really afraid of being judged.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.23,0:16:42.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可我并沒有感到驚訝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It didn't surprise me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為這位男性朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}This is coming from my friend who,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:46.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在三四個星期之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}probably three or four weeks ago,
