Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他認識所有人  大家也都知道他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He knew everybody, and everybody knew him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.49,0:16:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為總和他在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I felt like my popularity scale rose
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.20,0:17:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得自己也變得出名了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}just because I hung out with him.
