Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.75,0:21:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有個想法\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We had this idea
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.47,0:21:47.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓湯姆和謝恩相互認識一下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that we had to get Tom and Shane to meet each other.
