Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她跟我說有個叫湯姆的人也會去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She said that there was gonna be this guy there named Tom
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.77,0:21:58.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在這個行業中十分活躍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and that he's active in the industry,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.17,0:21:59.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}《新聞周刊》平面模特照
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:22:01.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她覺得結識他  會對我今后的發展有幫助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So she thought that maybe it would be a good person to be connected with.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.07,0:22:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們到了那里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.18,0:22:05.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他非常引人注目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He is ridiculously attractive --
