Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.94,0:22:19.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord1\shad0\fn方正准圆_GBK\b1\c&H101514&\b1\4c&H000000&\fs18\t(0,0,1,\fs21)\fad(0,0)\move(114,71.642,101.222,41.552))}{\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\c&H1A0914&}我們喜歡這些男人
