Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:19.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他開始問"這家伙是誰"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was like, "who is this guy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.68,0:22:22.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我反問他"他為何讓你如此糾結  謝恩"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I'm like, "why is he bothering you so much, Shane?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.12,0:22:24.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他比我大四歲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was four years older than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.54,0:22:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去過很多地方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Like, he had traveled the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.51,0:22:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會說外語\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}you know, spoke a different language.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.10,0:22:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會演奏好幾種樂器\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He played a bunch of instruments.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他總是自信滿滿的樣子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was just so cocky and confident,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.41,0:22:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然  保齡球也打得很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and, well, of course, he, like, was bowling really well.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.51,0:22:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我  連五個瓶都擊不倒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And then here I am, like, can't even knock five pins down.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.60,0:22:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在打完保齡球不久之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So, it wasn't too long after we went bowling
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.41,0:22:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們又在我朋友莉茲的公寓里碰到了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that we all got together again at my friend Lizzy's apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.58,0:22:45.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那天晚上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was that night
