Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.63,0:22:49.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們一起出去玩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We ended up hanging out,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.31,0:22:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四處周游\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}you know, a few times here and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.05,0:22:53.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直唱歌  總是很開心的樣子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And he was always singing. He was always happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.90,0:22:56.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}?生活就像高速公路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}♪ Life is a highway
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.51,0:23:00.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}?我要星夜兼程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}♪ I want to ride it all night long
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.64,0:23:02.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和湯姆  我們白天一直待在一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Tom and I, we would spend all day together,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.04,0:23:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后他回自己家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and then he would go home,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.04,0:23:06.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后  晚上的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}which would lead to, later in the evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.97,0:23:08.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們還要講上幾個小時的電話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}talking on the phone for a few hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.09,0:23:10.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒過多久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It did not take long
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.32,0:23:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就覺得與湯姆相處很愉快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}for me to really feel comfortable with Tom,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.97,0:23:15.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以對他無所不談\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that I could tell him anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.66,0:23:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以信任他一輩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Like, I trusted him with my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆是個很自信的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Tom was a very confident person.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.44,0:23:23.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他主動追求謝恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He went after Shane.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.19,0:23:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,起初  謝恩的反應是"天吶"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}At first, Shane was like, "aah,"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:27.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他從沒談過戀愛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}'cause he had never been in a relationship before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.53,0:23:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這對他來說是初戀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}This was his, you know, first love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.73,0:23:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們有次去聽湯姆演唱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We went to hear Tom one time,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.02,0:23:36.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝恩會在他表演的時候環顧四周\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and Shane would look around the room while he was playing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.07,0:23:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他想讓所有人都專心聽他唱歌\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}because he wanted to make sure everybody was paying attention
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.53,0:23:43.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并對他同樣狂熱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and seeing what he saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.05,0:23:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一個猶太單詞叫做自豪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And there is a Jewish word called kvell.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.14,0:23:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那正是湯姆表演時他臉上的神情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And that's what he looked like when Tom performed --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.67,0:23:51.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他無比自豪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}he was kvelling.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.59,0:23:53.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱情洋溢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was glowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.58,0:23:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,終于體驗到愛情的滋味非常美妙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was incredible to finally experience that feeling of love,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.44,0:23:59.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有如心花怒放一般\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}you know, like the butterflies.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這正是我想象中我的朋友們有過的感受\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's what I always imagined that all my friends felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.29,0:24:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒過多久  我就搬進了他的公寓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It didn't take long for me to move into his apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.66,0:24:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們很快就走到了一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They got very close very quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.71,0:24:10.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為他們能走到一起并不是因為搬去了洛杉磯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I think their freedom wasn't moving to L.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.70,0:24:13.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是由于湯姆為謝恩創造了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I think Tom was definitely the door for Shane
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.79,0:24:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認同自己的機會\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to come to terms with himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.65,0:24:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆是他的避風港\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Tom was a safe place.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.17,0:24:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆認識謝恩的時候  他就像只迷失的羊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}When Tom met Shane, he was a little, lost sheep.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.47,0:24:25.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆真的把謝恩照顧的很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And Tom really looked out for Shane.
