Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.66,0:35:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是像學生一樣旅游\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They would travel like they were students.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.86,0:35:30.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我記得他們第一次旅行是去埃及\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The first trip I remember them taking was to Egypt,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.39,0:35:31.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沿尼羅河而下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}down the Nile.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.77,0:35:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}?你是我的專屬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}♪ You belong to me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.04,0:35:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那并不是我會選擇的旅行方式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But it wasn't the kind of trip that I would have gone on.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.15,0:35:39.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}?沒有你我是如此孤單\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}♪ I'd be so alone without you
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.01,0:35:38.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們睡在用屏風隔開的甲板上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They slept on the deck with canvas dividers,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.45,0:35:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蓋著毯子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}covered in blankets,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.41,0:35:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆還得了肺炎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and Tom caught pneumonia,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.60,0:35:42.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他們真的度過了一段美好時光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but they had one heck of a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.22,0:35:46.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}?或許你也會孤單沮喪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}♪ Maybe you'd be lonesome too and blue
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.89,0:35:52.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}?在回家之前你要記得\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}♪ Just remember till you're home again
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.84,0:35:58.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}?你是我的專屬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}♪ You belong to me
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.42,0:35:58.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和湯姆進展到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Tom and I reached a point where
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.76,0:36:01.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他準備跟我回蒙大拿州的階段\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}we were ready for him to come to Montana.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.15,0:36:03.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總跟他說蒙大拿州有多美\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You know, I kept talking about how beautiful Montana is.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.77,0:36:06.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但對于我來說  更激動的是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But for me, it was more about -- you know, I was just excited
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.12,0:36:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他終于要見我家人了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}for him to finally meet my entire family.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.57,0:36:11.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的父親  干了一輩子伐木工\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}My dad, all his life, was a logger.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.52,0:36:13.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他會開同性戀的玩笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I mean, he told gay jokes --
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.44,0:36:16.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那種可以跟他坐下來說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}not the type of person that you could sit down and be like,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.28,0:36:17.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"喂  你兒子是同性戀"之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}"Hey, your son's gay,"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.75,0:36:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他還能坦然接受的那種人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and he would take it easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.51,0:36:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次見到湯姆時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The first time I ever met Tom,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.56,0:36:23.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我剛從鎮上回來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I had just been to town,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.64,0:36:27.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到我女兒的車停在車道上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and I had seen my daughter's car in the driveway.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.00,0:36:31.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝恩和湯姆趕緊躲進了柜子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So Shane and Tom jumped in the closet to hide,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.87,0:36:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an1\bord0\shad2\fn方正兰亭特黑_GBK\b1\c&HFFFFFF&\fs24\4c&H000000&\fad(800,800)\pos(40.167,214)}杰西 {\fn方正兰亭黑_GBK\fs20}謝恩的姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.83,0:36:33.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爸走進來時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and then my dad walks in,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.64,0:36:36.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他倆就一起跳出來大喊 "想不到吧"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and they both jump out of the closet like, "Surprise!"
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.28,0:36:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,結果是我的兒子和他的伴侶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And here's my boy, and here's his partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.90,0:36:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們成功了  我確實沒想到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And it worked -- they surprised me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.35,0:36:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都覺得這真是太搞笑了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And we just thought it was funnier than hell that they did that,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.66,0:36:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他們真是從柜子里跳出來"出柜"的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}because it's like they came out of the closet at my dad's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.22,0:36:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆知道我有大男子主義\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Tom, he knew I was a macho-type guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.70,0:36:54.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可能會有大男子主義的保守觀念\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and maybe that I was gonna have the macho-type conservatism
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.90,0:36:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,認為我不會接納他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that wouldn't accept him,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.89,0:36:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能夠看得出他為此花的心思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and you could just see he tried all the time around me.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.25,0:37:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很感激他做的努力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I appreciated that -- him trying,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.87,0:37:02.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,努力讓自己變得討喜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}him trying to be likeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.53,0:37:03.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜歡上湯姆是件很容易的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was easy to like Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.82,0:37:04.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是一個很棒的小伙子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was a great guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.01,0:37:06.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆很有魅力\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Tom was a pistol.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.03,0:37:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是個很有趣的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He was so much fun to be around.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.99,0:37:11.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我見過他逗謝恩大笑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I saw that he made Shane laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.19,0:37:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那種快樂是你在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It's the type of happiness you have
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.08,0:37:14.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遇到靈魂伴侶后才會有的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}when you meet your soul mate.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.87,0:37:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這讓我之前的擔心云消霧散\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And that made all my worries just disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.17,0:37:21.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆跟我回亞利桑那州看望我的祖父母\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So, Tom and I went to Arizona to visit my grandparents.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.32,0:37:23.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝恩非常開心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Shane was so happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.58,0:37:25.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是他長大之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was the happiest that I'd ever seen him,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.81,0:37:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我見他最開心的一次\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}since he was a little kid on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.90,0:37:30.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的曾祖母帕特也在\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And my Great-grandma Pat was there.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.24,0:37:32.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒人告訴她我跟湯姆是情侶\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And no one told Grandma Pat that Tom and I were a couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.93,0:37:34.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說  "很高興見到你啊"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She was like, "Oh, nice to meet you."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.36,0:37:37.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后  我聽到她在另一間房里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And then, later, I heard her in the other room
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.08,0:37:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,問我的祖母朱迪  "那人是誰啊"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}ask my Grandma Judy like, "So, who was that guy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.21,0:37:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道謝恩是同性戀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Well, I never knew Shane was gay,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.10,0:37:43.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但當我見到他伴侶時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but I met his partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.24,0:37:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得他是個不錯的小伙子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and he was a very nice guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.63,0:37:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都很喜歡他  我覺得沒什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and we all liked him and went along fine with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.32,0:37:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆迷上帕特祖母是有原因的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Tom was fascinated with Grandma Pat for a few reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.08,0:37:54.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,每一年  她都會記錄自己殺了多少條蛇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You know, every year, she keeps track of how many snakes she kills.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.65,0:37:57.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我總是跟蛇過不去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Well, I'm always after a snake --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.29,0:37:58.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不希望它們出現在附近\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't want them around.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.24,0:38:02.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你每年春天最多能殺多少條蛇來著\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I mean, you killed up to how many in a spring -- every spring?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.71,0:38:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能有40條甚至更多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Oh, I killed up to 40 or better.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.56,0:38:08.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一次我和湯姆陪兩個祖母去散步\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}After Tom and I went for a walk with both of my grandmas,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.22,0:38:09.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在回家的路上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}when we were coming back into the house,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.86,0:38:11.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特祖母摟著湯姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Grandma Pat like put her arm around Tom.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.97,0:38:14.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說  "歡迎加入這個大家庭"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She was like, "Welcome to the family."
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.02,0:38:15.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她已經九十歲了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She's 90 years old,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.60,0:38:18.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但仍然能接納了我們的關系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and, you know, she's accepting our relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.23,0:38:20.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對他們品頭論足的那些人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}People that talk about them,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.57,0:38:22.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們對此一知半解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}they don't understand a lot of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.69,0:38:25.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們認為  如果他倆去教堂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And they think that, if they go to church and everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.72,0:38:28.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上帝自會懲罰他們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that God will take care of it --
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.60,0:38:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像懲罰其他同性戀一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They can be just like all the rest of the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.07,0:38:32.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以你沒法說服他們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And so you can't get through to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.15,0:38:35.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說實話  那些話我都聽膩了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}To tell you the truth, I'm tired of hearing about it --
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.84,0:38:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們的確不是羅密歐與茱麗葉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So they're not Romeo and Juliet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.09,0:38:40.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯  他們是羅密歐與羅密歐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}That's right -- they're Romeo and Romeo.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.44,0:38:41.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多大事啊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Get over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.42,0:38:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不喜歡在公共場合表露自己的情感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I did not like to show any public display of affection --
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.04,0:38:50.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是坐在飛機上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Whether it would be us on a plane flying somewhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.85,0:38:53.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們想親熱時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and we wanted to be affectionate,
