Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.53,0:45:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在那時  我開始著急了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So at that moment is when my heart just started racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.09,0:45:41.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跑到樓下的時候  他趴在地上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}By the time I got there, he's on, you know, his stomach.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.14,0:45:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我撫摸著他的背\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I'm rubbing his back.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.12,0:45:46.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  "沒事的  湯米  沒事的"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I'm saying, "It's okay, Tommy. It's okay, Tommy."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.32,0:45:48.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而我穿的像個妓女\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Meanwhile, I look like a total hooker.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.43,0:45:52.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,救護車過了好久才到\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But it takes forever for the ambulance to get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.92,0:45:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多過了有25分鐘吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I want to say 25 minutes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.65,0:45:57.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們問我  "你有他的身份證件嗎"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They were like, "Do you have his I.D.?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.35,0:45:58.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"你有他的身份證件嗎"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Do you have his I.D.?"
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.32,0:46:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  "身份證有那么重要嗎"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I was like, "What the fuck does it matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.44,0:46:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"趕緊把他抬上救護車呀"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Just get him on the ambulance!"
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.69,0:46:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我趕到急診室\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So, I got to the E.R.,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.75,0:46:05.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們把我帶到艾麗克斯的房間\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and they took me into a room where Alex was,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.29,0:46:07.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她情緒很激動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and she was hysterical.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.10,0:46:08.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一看到謝恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And when I first saw Shane,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.79,0:46:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  "要是墜樓的是我就好了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I said, "I wish it were me."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.64,0:46:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  "因為你們擁有彼此"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I said, "Because you two have each other,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.95,0:46:24.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"你倆愛得那么死去活來"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}"and the love you have is so strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:24.15,0:46:27.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我真希望掉下去的是我"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I wish it had been me who fell over."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.76,0:46:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我問她  "現在是什么狀況"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I asked her, you know, "Well, what's happening?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.47,0:46:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他們還在搶救嗎"  我完全不知情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}are they working on him?" I didn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.11,0:46:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她也一無所知\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And she didn't know anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.38,0:46:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們抱在一起  說愛著對方\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We hugged, you know, and we said we loved each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.88,0:46:44.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我仍抱有希望  覺得他會沒事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I was still hanging on to hope that he was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:44.56,0:46:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我試著給謝恩打電話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I tried calling Shane,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.38,0:46:47.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但總聯系不上他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and I couldn't get through to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.03,0:46:49.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,后來  他終于給我回了電話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And, finally, he calls me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.65,0:46:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說  "媽  湯姆去拍照"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He said, "Mom, Tom was doing a photo shoot,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.82,0:46:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"從屋頂上墜樓了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and he fell off the roof."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.80,0:46:54.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  "天吶"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I just -- "Oh, my god."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.38,0:46:55.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  "親愛的  要一直祈禱"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I said, "Honey, just keep on praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.62,0:46:58.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他會沒事的  咱們都會為他祈禱的" \N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He'll be fine. You know, we'll get the prayers going here."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.22,0:47:01.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我收到謝恩的短信說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I got a text message from Shane saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.22,0:47:04.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"米凱拉  求你快祈禱  湯姆受傷了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}"Michaela, please pray -- Tom's hurt."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.76,0:47:09.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我立刻跪在地上  開始祈禱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I immediately got down and started praying.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.26,0:47:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,過了一會兒  他打給我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So, a little bit later, he calls me,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.66,0:47:14.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說  "媽  他們不讓我進去看他"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and he says, "Mom, they won't let me in to see him."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.98,0:47:16.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我問  "怎么會這樣"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I said, "Well, how come?"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.75,0:47:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們說  "因為我不是他的家屬"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And they said, "Because I'm not family."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.71,0:47:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  "天吶  謝恩"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I just -- "Oh, my God, Shane."
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.06,0:47:23.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我打給了湯姆的母親\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So, I called Tom's mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.44,0:47:26.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那時印第安納州已是深夜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And it's, you know, late at night in Indiana.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.16,0:47:29.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一開口便問道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And, you know, the first thing she says was,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.33,0:47:31.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他喝了多少酒  謝恩"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}"Well, how much was he drinking, Shane?"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.50,0:47:34.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能聽到他爸在后面說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And then his dad, in the background, was saying,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.71,0:47:37.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他跑到屋頂上去做什么"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}"Well, what the hell was he doing on the roof?"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.91,0:47:40.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,隨后  我就把電話給了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I just, from that point forward, I made sure
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.38,0:47:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在場的醫護人員  讓他們說了情況\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to let the nursing staff or the doctors speak to her and to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.13,0:47:47.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等了差不多一小時之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And it had been probably about an hour later,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.99,0:47:50.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫生來到我們的房間\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}the doctor came into the room,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.87,0:47:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我立馬就知道了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and, like, I just, I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.12,0:48:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道他要說些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Like, I knew what he was gonna say.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.65,0:48:05.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當他開始講話的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And when he was talking,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.68,0:48:07.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我跟本什么都沒聽進去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}like, it wasn't registering in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.89,0:48:10.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像左耳進右耳出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Like, I wasn't processing what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.63,0:48:12.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他說他沒挺過來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He just said he didn't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.40,0:48:14.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的非常...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And it was very, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:15.15,0:48:18.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們都失聲痛哭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And we all just lost it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.53,0:48:22.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我必須離開那個房間  因為我真得聽不下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I had to just leave the room because I couldn't hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.03,0:48:25.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾麗克斯一直在哭  她不停地做這個動作\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Alex was crying, and she was continually doing this --
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.57,0:48:28.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想她受了很大的打擊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I think because she was just so traumatized.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.45,0:48:32.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾麗克斯的媽媽不停的說  "天吶"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And Alex's Mom was saying, "Oh, my god."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.57,0:48:33.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"天吶"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}"Oh, my god."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.26,0:48:36.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是  "他可憐的媽媽"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And sometimes she would say, "Oh, his mother."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.30,0:48:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為第二天就是母親節\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}'Cause Mother's Day was the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.61,0:48:41.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我走出房間\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So, I went outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.01,0:48:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我媽打了電話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I called my mom, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.03,0:48:49.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  "媽  他走了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I was like, "Mom, he died."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.33,0:48:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說  "我很遺憾  謝恩"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And, you know, she just said, "I'm so sorry, Shane.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.75,0:48:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"真的很遺憾"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'm so sorry."
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.12,0:48:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一直在哭  我也在哭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And he was just crying, and I'm crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.92,0:49:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但再一次  你卻在2400公里之外\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And, you know, here you are, again, 1,500 miles away,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.01,0:49:01.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無法陪著自己的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and you can't be there for your child.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.53,0:49:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接到了他的電話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I got ahold of him,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.61,0:49:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說湯姆在醫院里去世了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and Tom had just died in the hospital, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:09.93,0:49:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我永遠不想再回憶這個時刻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I don't know. It's not a moment I want to ever go through again.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.10,0:49:17.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有什么比這更痛苦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The worst pain I have ever felt in my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.51,0:49:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的腦子一片空白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Like, I just sunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.50,0:49:22.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我說  "你他媽開玩笑吧"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I just said, "Are you fucking kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.67,0:49:25.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"真的嗎"  我說  "真的嗎  誰會這樣死掉"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Seriously?" I said, "Seriously, who dies like that?"
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.81,0:49:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為在他斷氣的瞬間\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I figured Shane was probably there when he passed,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.22,0:49:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝恩會陪在他床邊  緊握他的手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}by his bed, holding his hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.71,0:49:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他卻說沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And he said no.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.38,0:49:38.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于是我沖向護士站  我說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So, I went to the nurse's station, and I said,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:38.41,0:49:42.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我朋友的男朋友在這"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}"You know, my friend's boyfriend is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.23,0:49:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他剛剛去世  能讓他們見最后一面嗎"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He just passed away. Can you take him back?"
Dialogue: 0,0:49:45.21,0:49:49.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她卻說  "在他父母來這之前"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And she said, "We can't allow non-family members to see him
