Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.18,0:54:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝恩一直很配合她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Shane was more than willing to work with her,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:56.88,0:54:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她想要的湯姆的東西都給了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}give her anything she wanted of Tom's,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.57,0:55:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但這侵犯了他的隱私\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but it started to invade his privacy,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.53,0:55:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而他對此毫不抱怨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and he wouldn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.08,0:55:07.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪莎會就一些東西說三道四\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Martha would make a comment about something,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:07.16,0:55:09.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而謝恩則收起了一切感情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and Shane would just stuff the emotions away,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.56,0:55:11.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像小時候孩子們給他起外號時一樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}like back when kids would call him names.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.75,0:55:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無權說任何話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I couldn't say anything, anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.52,0:55:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我無權阻止她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I had no legal right to stop her.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.70,0:55:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆的媽媽和我們一起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So, Tom's mom was waiting, along with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.01,0:55:22.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等著驗尸官移交他的遺體\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}for the coroner to release his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:22.04,0:55:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,介于這次意外的情況\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Due to the circumstances of the accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.60,0:55:26.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他的遺體必須進行尸檢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}they had to do an autopsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.76,0:55:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們開始討論起葬禮的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We started talking about the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.54,0:55:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說  不  我們都會被邀請參加\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And she said that, no, we're all invited.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.68,0:55:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可以住在他們家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We could stay at their house.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.59,0:55:34.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為家屬出席葬禮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You know, "Come as a family.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.09,0:55:36.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們會一起舉行葬禮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}We'll just do all this together."
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.36,0:55:41.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一直在說  "我要帶我的寶貝回家"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She was very, you know, "I'm taking my baby home.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:41.23,0:55:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"你們都要來  我希望你們出席"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}You guys are all coming with. I want you to be there."
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.71,0:55:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而隨著一天天的等待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And then, as the days go on,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.05,0:55:47.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不再談論葬禮的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}she pretty much quit talking about the funeral
Dialogue: 0,0:55:47.34,0:55:48.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不再提我們出席葬禮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and about us all going
Dialogue: 0,0:55:48.53,0:55:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與東部家鄉的親人一起悼念湯姆的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and sharing Tom with everybody back east.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:53.06,0:55:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆的母親待在另一個房間\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Tom's mom was in the other room or even sometimes
Dialogue: 0,0:55:55.85,0:55:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甚至有時就坐在我旁邊策劃葬禮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}right next to me making the funeral arrangements
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.42,0:56:02.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卻不讓我參與其中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and planning it all out, and I was not a part of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.76,0:56:05.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像我是空氣  是幽靈\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was like I wasn't there. It was like I was a ghost.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.00,0:56:08.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是一位剛剛失去兒子的母親\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She was a mother who'd just lost her son --
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.31,0:56:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她那20多歲的兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}her 20-something-year-old son --
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.06,0:56:14.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除了悲傷  你不能指望她有其他的情緒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So there were no expectations other than grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.32,0:56:18.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我沒想到她會傷害謝恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But I didn't think that she was gonna hurt Shane.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.02,0:56:20.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以為她愛謝恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I thought that she loved Shane.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.67,0:56:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得肯定有什么不對勁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The feeling I got was something was awry,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:24.77,0:56:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但沒人會指責她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}but nobody could put their finger on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.53,0:56:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后到了周四早上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And then, that Thursday morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:29.09,0:56:30.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪莎突然說  "我要離開了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Martha was like, "I got to go."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:30.22,0:56:31.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝恩說  "我開車送你去機場"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And Shane's like, "I'll drive you to the airport."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:31.82,0:56:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說  "不  我坐出租車"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She's like, "No, I'll get a taxi."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.17,0:56:35.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告訴她  "我不會讓你坐出租車的"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I told her, "I'm not gonna let you take a taxi."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.74,0:56:37.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有一種預感\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I kind of had a feeling
Dialogue: 0,0:56:37.48,0:56:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她知道一些我不知道的事情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that she knew something that I didn't know,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.13,0:56:44.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她知道湯姆的遺體隨時可以移交\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that she knew that his body was gonna be released any moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.23,0:56:48.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她打包了湯姆的所有衣物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She was packing all Tom's clothes up
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.10,0:56:49.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好讓其陪著他長眠于地下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that she was gonna bury him in,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.42,0:56:51.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而她準備給他遺體穿上的夾克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and the jacket that she wanted to put him in
Dialogue: 0,0:56:51.38,0:56:53.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,則沒有放進行李箱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}was not fitting in the suitcase.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:53.66,0:56:55.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝恩說  "沒關系  瑪莎"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And Shane's like, "It's okay, Martha.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.19,0:56:57.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我到時候帶過去"  但她卻說  "不"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I'll just bring it." And she was like, "No.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.22,0:56:58.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"絕對不行"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Absolutely not."
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.28,0:57:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在回過頭看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So, maybe looking back now,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.39,0:57:05.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可能就是要發生的事件的征兆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}it could have been foreshadowing what could have happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.86,0:57:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她那時候就知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that she knew then
Dialogue: 0,0:57:07.02,0:57:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她不會讓謝恩參加葬禮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}that she wasn't gonna let Shane come to the funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.07,0:57:13.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我把她送到目的地  擁抱了她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I dropped her off, and we hugged.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.29,0:57:16.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請求她有什么情況及時通知我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I asked her to please keep me updated
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.14,0:57:17.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以便我知曉那邊的情況\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}so I know what's happening,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.24,0:57:19.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她答應我會那樣做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and she promised me that she would.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.70,0:57:22.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我再也沒有聽到她的消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}But I never heard from her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.41,0:57:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很感激我們為她兒子做的一切\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She was so grateful and so loving towards us
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.13,0:57:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她對我們十分友善\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}for everything that we did for her son.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.92,0:57:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她一直哭  擁抱我們  拉著我們的手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}She just was crying and hugging us and holding on to us
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.13,0:57:33.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說什么"我希望成為你們生活的一部分"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and, "I want to be a part of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.40,0:57:35.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我想常來拜訪"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I want to come visit."
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.06,0:57:38.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺我們和她建立了感情\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}It was like we were bonded with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.23,0:57:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了第二天  她就不見了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And then, the next day, she was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.63,0:57:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湯姆去世的第二天  我跟他媽媽通過話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I talked to Tom's mom the day after he died.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.26,0:57:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她說  "一旦葬禮定好時間"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And she said, "I'll let you know
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.55,0:57:47.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"我會及時通知你"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}as soon as I know when the funeral is gonna be
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.92,0:57:48.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"好讓你能夠出席"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}so that you can be there."
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.72,0:57:51.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后就什么動靜也沒有了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Then, it was pretty much radio silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.20,0:57:52.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們沒回電告訴我葬禮什么時候舉行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They never called me back to tell me when it was,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.72,0:57:54.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我很受傷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and I was very hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.13,0:57:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到了報紙上的告示\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I see the notice in the newspaper --
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.98,0:58:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}他去世后留下了父母諾曼和瑪莎  姐姐金和哥哥大衛\N可通過殯儀館向此家庭捐贈
Dialogue: 0,0:57:55.90,0:57:58.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,守靈是當天  葬禮是第二天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Wake is this day. Funeral is the next day.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.35,0:58:02.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給湯姆家打電話確認\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I called Tom's house to verify,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:02.77,0:58:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接電話的親戚說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and, you know, the relative who answered just said,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.92,0:58:06.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"如果報紙上這么說"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}"If that's what the paper says,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:06.95,0:58:08.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"那應該沒錯"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}then I would probably go by that."
Dialogue: 0,0:58:08.57,0:58:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后我親自給\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I personally called back
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.10,0:58:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他家鄉不同的太平間打電話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to different mortuaries in his hometown
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.06,0:58:15.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,試圖確認這一消息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}to try to get information,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.58,0:58:17.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可沒人愿意告訴我們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and nobody would give us any information.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:18.22,0:58:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盡管我們再沒聽到瑪莎的回音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}So, although I never heard from Martha,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.73,0:58:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我媽媽  艾麗克斯和我還是訂了機票\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}my mom and Alex and I, we all booked our plane tickets.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.72,0:58:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在中途停留時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}During our layover,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.37,0:58:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我接到了湯姆親戚打來的電話\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I received a phone call from one of Tom's relatives.
