Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.27,1:00:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9}?如果再給我一天生命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}♪ If I could have one more day
