Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.04,1:00:31.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得這些能反映出這個家庭的情況\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I think it was very reflective of the family
