Dialogue: 0,1:00:35.98,1:00:37.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當我起身走到瑪莎身邊時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}When I got up to Martha,
