Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.03,1:00:51.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葬禮上描述的湯姆\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}The funeral depicted Tom
