Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.21,1:01:03.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我從2000級送的花束中拿走了幾支花\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}I took the flowers from the bouquet that the class of 2000 sent,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.90,1:01:06.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將其風干  以便我能送給謝恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}and I dried them so I could give those to Shane.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.36,1:01:07.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給他留了份葬禮流程單\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I saved him a program
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.77,1:01:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為他是湯姆此身的摯愛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}because, you know, he is the love of Tom's life.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.59,1:01:12.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他值得擁有這些東西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}He at least deserves that.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.33,1:01:14.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不幸的是  其中并有沒提及他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Unfortunately, he wasn't mentioned in it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.34,1:01:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了將近30年的親人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}Families, for literally 30 years,
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.48,1:01:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以藏匿秘密  直到有人死去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}can sweep that secret under the rug until someone dies,
