Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.22,1:01:26.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為湯姆的父母就是這樣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}And I think that's what happened to Tom's parents.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.62,1:01:28.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們有個很棒的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H000000&}{\shad1}They had this great child.
